      <h1>How Brands Build Trust and Credibility Through Video</h1>
      <p class="lead">Build trust and credibility with authentic video content. Learn how Viven helps your brand connect and grow.</p>
      <p class="post-meta"><span>Sofia Treviño</span> <span>·</span> <span>October 21, 2024</span> <span>·</span> <span>Updated March 18, 2025</span></p>
