<!-- ============ ARTICLE ============ -->
<section class="sec" style="padding-top:40px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="post-wrap post-body reveal">
<p>Brands build trust and credibility through video by showing real customers, real employees, and real moments instead of scripted claims — authenticity is what convinces buyers to act. In a study by Edelman, 81% of consumers said they need to trust a brand before buying from it, and video is one of the most effective ways to earn that trust at scale. At Viven, we partner with businesses to produce video content that fosters confidence and builds lasting trust with customers.</p><h2>Why Trust Matters</h2><p>Authentic videos showing product use, customer testimonials, and behind-the-scenes footage create the trust customers need to make purchasing decisions. Without that trust, even the best product struggles to convert interest into sales, no matter how strong the underlying offer is. Buyers today can research a company from every angle, so the brands that show up honestly on video tend to win the benefit of the doubt earlier in that process.</p><h2>Viven Delivers Authentic Content</h2><p>At Viven, we specialize in delivering authentic <a href={p("services/brand-video")}>video content</a> that resonates with audiences. From real customer stories to unscripted testimonials, we help brands create videos that reflect honesty and transparency — essential ingredients for trust-building. That means resisting the urge to over-script, and instead letting real employees and customers speak in their own words.</p><h3>Trust-Building Videos Viven Offers</h3><ul><li>Customer testimonial videos</li><li>Behind-the-scenes production videos</li><li>Company culture videos</li><li>CEO message videos</li></ul><h2>Case Study: Trust and Credibility with SV Group</h2><p>SV Group, a prominent hospitality and gastronomy company, partnered with Viven to produce a video that showcased the company's dynamic work environment and the synergy between their IT and operations teams. The video was part of an <a href={p("services/employer-branding")}>employer branding</a> and recruitment campaign, aimed at highlighting the authenticity of their culture.</p><p>The result: the video helped SV Group build trust with potential recruits, leading to a significant increase in high-quality applications. It showcased the company's culture while reinforcing its credibility as a transparent, professional employer — proof that a single well-produced video can move a genuinely hard business metric like applicant quality.</p><h2>Build Trust With Video</h2><p>Trust doesn't come from claims — it comes from proof, told through the people who live it every day. If you want to go deeper on why testimonials in particular are so persuasive, see why <a href={p("blog/why-customer-testimonial-videos-are-a-game-changer-for-big-brands")}>customer testimonial videos are a game changer for brands</a>, and why they're becoming <a href={p("blog/testimonials-the-most-trusted-marketing-tool-in-2025")}>the most trusted marketing tool in 2025</a>.</p><p><a href={p("contact")}>Work with Viven</a> to create video content that builds trust for your brand.</p>
    </div>
    <p class="post-service-note"><a href={p("services/brand-video")}>Want to see how this works in practice? Explore our brand video production.</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

